---------------------------------
Posts API
---------------------------------
###
Create a New Post
POST http://localhost:3000/posts/createPost
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first post.",
  "sender": "Osher"
}

###
Get All Posts
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/getAllPosts

###
Get a Post by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/673cc241e8cf2cf4cf46298e

###
Get Posts by Sender
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?sender=Osher

###
Update a Post
PUT http://localhost:3000/posts/673cc241e8cf2cf4cf46298e
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Post Title",
  "content": "Updated content for the post."
}

