---------------------------------
Comments API
---------------------------------
Add a Comment to a Post
POST http://localhost:3000/comments/createComment
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "postId": "673cc241e8cf2cf4cf46298e",
    "content": "This is a comment on the post.",
    "author": "Alik"
}

###
Get a Comment by Sender
GET http://localhost:3000/comments/?sender=Alik

###

###
Get a Comment by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/comments/673cc337e8cf2cf4cf462990

###
Get All Comments for a Specific Post
GET http://localhost:3000/comments/673cc241e8cf2cf4cf46298e

###
Update a Comment
PUT http://localhost:3000/comments/673cc337e8cf2cf4cf462990
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated comment content."
}

###
Delete a Comment
DELETE http://localhost:3000/comments/673cc337e8cf2cf4cf462990
